\c 9
\s Mayelana lokunikela langesibusiso esivela ngokunikela
\p
\v 1 Ngoba mayelana lokuncedisa\x + 9.12,13. 8.4. Gal. 2.10.\x* okungokwabangcwele\x + Roma 12.13.\x* kakusweleki kimi ukulibhalela;
\v 2 ngoba ngiyazi ukukhuthala kwenu\x + 8.11.\x*, engizincoma ngakho\x + 8.24.\x* ngani kwabeMakedoniya, ukuthi iAkaya\x + Roma 15.26. Seb. 18.12.\x* yayisizilungisele kusukela nyakenye\x + 8.10.\x*; lokutshiseka okuvela kini kubavusile abanengi.
\v 3 Kodwa ngithume abazalwane\x + 9.5. 8.23.\x*, ukuze ukuzincoma kwethu\x + 1.14.\x* ngani kungenziwa ize maqondana lalokhu\x + 3.10.\x*; ukuze, njengokutsho kwami, libe lilungile\x + 1 Kor. 16.2.\x*;
\v 4 hlezi mhlawumbe, nxa abeMakedoniya befika lami\x + Seb. 20.4.\x* belifica lingalungiselanga, siyangeke thina (ukuze singatsho, lina) ngalesisibindi sokuzincoma\x + 11.17.\x*\x + Heb. 3.14.\x*.
\v 5 Ngakho ngibona kufanele ukuthi ngikhuthaze abazalwane\x + 9.5. 8.23.\x*, ukuze baqale ukuza kini, njalo balungisele ngaphambili ukupha kwenu ngesihle\f + \fk ukupha ngesihle: \fl kumbe, \fq isibusiso.\f* okwakhulunywa ngakho mandulo, ukuthi lesi silungile, ngokunjalo njengesibusiso\x + Fil. 4.17.\x* futhi kungenjengokuncitshana\x + 12.17.\x*.
\p
\v 6 Lalokhu \add ukuthi\add*, ohlanyela ingcosana, laye uzavuna ingcosana\x + Gal. 6.7,9. Zaga 11.18,24,25. Zaga 19.17.\x*; lohlanyela ngokunengi, laye uzavuna ngokunengi.
\v 7 Ngulowo lalowo njengalokhu azikhethela khona enhliziyweni; kungabi ngokokudonda\x + Dute. 15.7.\x*\x + Dute. 15.10.\x* kumbe ngokokubanjwa ngamandla; ngoba uNkulunkulu\x + 8.12. Zaga 22.8. Roma 12.8. Eks. 25.2.\x* uyamthanda onikela ngentokozo.
\v 8 Njalo uNkulunkulu\x + Gal. 6.7,9. Zaga 11.18,24,25. Zaga 19.17.\x*\x + Fil. 4.19.\x* ulamandla okulengezelela wonke umusa\x + 1 Kor. 16.3.\x*, ukuze, lilokwenela konke ezintweni zonke ngesikhathi sonke, lengezwe emisebenzini yonke emihle\x + Seb. 9.36.\x*;
\v 9 njengokulotshiweyo \add ukuthi\add*: Uchithachithile\x + Hlab. 112.9.\x*, wanika abayanga; ukulunga kwakhe kuhlala kuze kube phakade.
\v 10 Njalo yena onika\x + Isa. 55.10.\x* inhlanyelo kumhlanyeli, lesinkwa sokudla, kwangathi anganika akhulise inhlanyelo yenu, andise izithelo\x + Luka 12.18. Hos. 10.12.\x* zokulunga kwenu\x + Mat. 6.1.\x*;
\v 11 linothiswe ezintweni zonke kukho konke ukuphana\f + \fk ukuphana: \fl kumbe, \fq inkululeko.\f*, okusebenza ngathi\x + 1.11.\x* ukubongwa kuNkulunkulu;
\v 12 ngoba umsebenzi\x + Luka 12.18. Hos. 10.12.\x* walinkonzo kawugcwalisi kuphela inswelo\x + 8.14.\x* zabangcwele, kodwa futhi wengeza ngokubongwa okunengi kuNkulunkulu\x + 1.11.\x*;
\v 13 ngobufakazi\x + 8.2. 8.8.\x* balinkonzo\x + 9.1.\x* badumisa uNkulunkulu\x + Gal. 1.24. 1 Pet. 2.12. Mat. 15.31. Mat. 5.16. Joha. 15.8.\x* ngokulalela kovumo\x + 10.5.\x* lwenu ivangeli likaKristu, langokupha \add kwenu\add* okukhulu\x + 9.11.\x* kubo, lakubo bonke;
\v 14 langomkhuleko wabo ngani, belilangatha ngomusa kaNkulunkulu\x + 8.1.\x* ongelakulinganiswa phezu kwenu.
\v 15 Njalo kabongwe uNkulunkulu\x + 8.1.\x* ngenxa yesipho sakhe esingakhulumekiyo.